word_group.brief_definition: 代替, 而不是, 取代

bilingual.source: Walk or ride a bike instead of taking a car.
bilingual.target: 步行或骑自行车代替开车。

bilingual.source: I will have tea instead of coffee.
You can use honey instead of syrup.
bilingual.target: 你可以用蜂蜜代替糖浆。

bilingual.source: You can use light soy sauce instead of salt.
She uses honey instead of sugar for baking.
bilingual.target: 她用蜂蜜代替糖来烘焙。

bilingual.source: She chose to walk instead of taking the bus.
bilingual.target: 她选择步行代替坐公交车。

bilingual.source: He decided to read a book instead of watching TV.
bilingual.target: 他决定读书代替看电视。

bilingual.source: Let's meet at the park instead of the mall.
bilingual.target: 我们在公园见面代替在商场见面。

bilingual.source: We use margarine instead of butter for baking.
bilingual.target: 我们用人造黄油代替黄油来烘焙。

bilingual.source: This recipe calls for a sweetener instead of sugar.
bilingual.target: 这个食谱要求用甜味剂代替糖。

list.abstract: instead（[ɪnˈsted]），英语单词，副词，词义为替代；顶替；代替。短语搭配有instead of（代替， 而不是，取代）。例句为“Instead, everything was run through virtual reality .（相反，一切都是通过虚拟现实运行的。）”

yingyinNormal.en: Road trip! Who wants to go instead of me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 公路旅行！谁想代替我去啊？

yingyinNormal.en: How about some food for thought instead? Don't drink. Keep your clothes on. Try avoiding those who might cause you to stray.
yingyinNormal.zh: 用精神食粮代替如何？别喝酒了，把衣服穿好，尝试避开那些会使你迷惘的人。

yingyinNormal.en: When our nation started the interstate highway act, instead of having local commerce, we could get goods coast to coast, top to bottom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当我们的国家开始实施了州际高速公路法案来代替当地的商业，我们可以获得商品东海岸到西海岸从上到下。

yingyinNormal.en: Can't I get a job instead?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不能在这儿工作吗？

yingyinNormal.en: You married him instead of me? Good call.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你拒绝我，却和这种人结婚？真不错。

yingyinNormal.en: What can I offer you instead of her? Nothing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 除了她，我还能给你什么？没了。

yingyinNormal.en: It's melted. How about ice-cream soup, instead?
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么都化了呢，要不然，给你来个冰淇淋汤怎么样？

yingyinNormal.en: What if I got married instead of going to college?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我不去上大学而是结婚 那会怎么样?

yingyinNormal.en: Instead of surfing channels, what about actually surfing?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不停转频道，还不如真的去冲浪吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Instead they farm the fish that's normally caught at sea.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不借助一船一线，而是采用渔场养殖那些通常要从海里捕获的鱼。

yingyinNormal.en: Strawberry. Oh, it's melted. How about ice-cream soup, instead?
yingyinNormal.zh: 草莓。噢，它化了。换成冰淇淋汤怎么样？

yingyinNormal.en: So why didn't you invite Conway? Brockhart was invited instead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你为什么不邀请康威？被邀请的是布洛哈特。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, like that, only instead of a chair, it's a pile of garbage. And instead of a jacket, it's a pile of garbage.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在她家是扔到一堆垃圾上，那也不是外套，而是一堆垃圾。

yingyinNormal.en: So why are you meeting me instead of at the Capitol?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那为什么约我来这里，而不是在国会？

yingyinNormal.en: I will, but instead i'm going to fire you as a client.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会的，不过我要做的是炒掉你这个客户。

yingyinNormal.en: He could have killed me, but instead he showed me mercy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他本来能杀了我，却选择了手下留情。

yingyinNormal.en: Instead you want me to slap you around like some animal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不说话，却想让我像畜生一样对你。

yingyinNormal.en: Then why did she come to him instead of him coming to her?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那为什么是她上门而不是他去找她？

yingyinNormal.en: Well, instead of just hanging out, we figure we'd do nothing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 与其待在一起胡混，我们决定这次什么也不做。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry you're here with me instead of Roger. Yeah, me too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可惜在这里的是我不是罗杰。就是啊。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Instead</highlight>, being grateful for small things every day is a much better way to improve wellbeing.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 相反，每天对小事心存感激是提升幸福感的更好方法。

examination_example.sentence: Buy all your clothes at once with a stylist <highlight>instead</highlight> of shopping alone, one article of clothing at a time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 和造型师一起一次性买下你所有的衣服，而不是一个人逛街，一次买一件衣服。

examination_example.sentence: It's also a good idea to shop daily <highlight>instead</highlight> of weekly, because, being human, you'll sometimes change your mind about what you fancy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 用每天购物代替每周购物也不失为一个好主意，因为作为人类，你的喜好有时候会变。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Instead</highlight>, they receive a fixed rate, which is typically about $825 for a standard four-hour vocal session.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 取而代之的是，他们会收到固定费率，对于一个标准的四小时人声会话，通常约为825美元。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Instead</highlight>, Rodriguez solicits residents' advice on what he should get on his cheeseburger and how he should spend the afternoon.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 取而代之的是，Rodriguez 向居民征求关于他该吃什么芝士汉堡以及如何度过下午的建议。

examination_example.sentence: He or she will <highlight>instead</highlight> point out, constructively and tactfully, exactly how their inflated sense of deservingness is somewhat distorted.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 相反，他们会建设性地、机智地指出，他们膨胀的应得感是如何被扭曲的。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Instead</highlight>, some in Africa and Asia are seeing their first light bulbs illuminated by the power of sunlight stored in batteries.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 相反，一些非洲和亚洲人见证了他们的第一个电灯泡是由存储在电池中的太阳能点亮的。

examination_example.sentence: Parents should <highlight>instead</highlight> watch with their kids and help them to understand the plot.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 父母应该和孩子一起观看，帮助他们理解故事情节。

examination_example.sentence: They prefer <highlight>instead</highlight> to slack off.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们反而更喜欢偷懒。

examination_example.sentence: The data set they used did not include economic data, so <highlight>instead</highlight> the researchers looked at whether the 2013-16 wellbeing decline was tracking economic indicators.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们使用的数据集不包括经济数据，因此研究人员研究了2013-16年的幸福感下降是否是在追随经济指标。

word_usage.usage:
instead是副词，后面不能直接跟宾语，多与介词of连用作为介词词组，后可跟宾语，表示“代替...”。
示例：我要这本书而不要那本。
误 I will take this book instead that one.
正 I will take this book instead of that one.

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation:
副词，常用于连接句子，可不译出，常放在句首或句尾，表示前面的事情没做，而做了后面的事。
例：He didn’t reply. Instead, he turned on his heel and left the room.
他没有回答，反而转身离开了房间。

是介词短语，其后要接词或词组。表示后面的事情没做，而做了前面的事。
例：You probably picked up my keys instead of yours.
你可能没拿你的钥匙而错拿了我的。
